entries.femaleVariant: Night City. Our home. Our pride.
From the moment I became your mayor, unemployment has dropped three percent and the murder rate by five.
But some cynics out there don't see Night City's beautiful potential as I do...
Do I love this city? Do I love its people? I have never loved anything--"
You placed your trust in me before. Let's work together again.
I'm Weldon Holt, and I approve this message.
